entry.tran: 舞台上天真少女的角色;扮演天真姑娘的女演员
entry.def: An ingenue is a young, innocent girl in a play or film, or an actress who plays the part of young, innocent girls.

example.ex: I don't want any more ingenue roles.
example.tran: 我不想再演天真少女的角色了。

means.word_mean: 1. an actress who specializes in playing the role of an artless innocent young girl
2. an artless innocent young girl (especially as portrayed on the stage)
3. the role of an innocent artless young woman in a play
